	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello. I just wanted to say, first of all, paladins ARE melee fighters. This is the problem with today's people. Most have been brainwashed into believing that they are "hybrids" and not "tanks." Well, you see, that is the POINT of a paladin. Paladins (and I'm not saying they do the most dmg) are THE tankers. So they may not be "melee fighters," but they sure as heck ARE "fighters." Us pallys are MEANT to be BUILT as a TANK rather than a "caster." They may be able to cast spells, but that doesn't mean that's something to build on. Paladins may be built as strong as warriors and as tough as them if only they follow the way of a warrior. Then they must believe that they're spell casting is an extra and almost pretend like they CAN'T give themselves more wis and such. IMO, we ARE the tanks of EQ.... When was the last time that group pulled a train and the WARRIOR stuck in there, got everything on him, then headed to zone and LIVED EVERY TIME! You've never seen that. Pallys (thanks to Lay Hands) are group savers. They're the ones that are meant to stay behind and take the dmg for the group. Paladins are excellent at soloing fyi also. Better than warriors, and sadly im not too sure about rangers or SK's. All you gotta do is pretend you are a warrior, go in there, fight till yer low on health, Root that bugger, back up and heal. And, if it happens to be that one hard guy and u just can't get him rooted... LAY HANDS!!! Ok, the other thing I wanted to add, is that I'm a 33 pally, and I have leveled up NO slower at all than my 34 druid. In fact, my 26 enchanter seems to be the "slow" leveler. Paladins do not seem to have an "exp restriction" whatsoever no matter what anyone says. Young paladins should not be discouraged by this statement that we gain exp slower. Because if it's true which i'm not sure... you DON'T notice it. If in fact it's true that u've never seen a dwarf pally, I suggest you change servers, cause if everyone's that dumb to make any other race paladin, you do NOT wanna be grouped with the people on that server. Those are the people who end up getting to 30 and deleting their pally. The majority of the higher level pallys ARE dwarfs, because only as a dwarf can one realize the true power of a pally. <br><br>Btw... what makes you think Freeport and Qeynos are the main paladin guilds? In my opinion, they're no different or WORSE than the kaladim pally guild. I love that place. Ok well if there's anything you would like to say in response to this, please respond.... I would love to argue about pallys! (for fun of course) =)<br><br>Gfuais Palais &lt;The Elderblood&gt;<br>Paladin of the 33rd Season<br>Follower of Brell on Drinal Server<br><br>aka<br><br>Uaieo Aieou &lt;The Elderblood&gt;<br>Enchanter of the 26th Season<br>Follower of Mithaniel Marr on Drinal Server<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
