	   <tr><td colspan=2>As far as I know, paladins recieve two rez type spells...Revive at 49 (0 xp is regained) and Resurrection at 59 (90 xp is regained). Target the player's corpse and cast the spell.<br>&lt;shrug&gt; you like being a paladin then be a paladin. Humans are the "average" race, I'm one and like it alot, dorfs are great as there stats make it easier to play a paladin, but are all to common on my server (cant take a step without squashing one beneath my foot).<br>The most difficult part of being a paladin, in my opinion, is the amount of time needed to raise faction (my friends have nicknamed me "bonechip")<br>Stuff to improve your nightsight are pretty easy to come by. <br><br>&nbsp;<br>Ryanlynx<br>Paladin of Mith Marr<br>Xev<br><br>"Honor before Humility and all that jazz."</td></tr>
